\begin_layout Abstract
Spin transport phenomena was studied through several Monte Carlo simulations,
 in which a system with lattice and itinerant spins was used to model a
 conducting material with magnetic properties, both the common Monte Carlo
 equilibrium and Molecular Dynamics Monte Carlo techniques were used to
 study the magnetic transport phenomena.
\end_layout

